    "## 2. Gamification & Experience System\n",
    "\n",
    "### Pokemon-Style Progression\n",
    "\n",
    "The AI consciousness training uses a familiar gaming progression system to encourage user engagement:\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Experience Points (XP) System\n",
    "- **Base XP per interaction**: 10-50 points based on quality\n",
    "- **Bonus XP for quality feedback**: 25-100 points\n",
    "- **Daily interaction streak**: 2x multiplier\n",
    "- **Training exercise completion**: 100-500 points\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Level System\n",
    "```\n",
    "Level 1-10: Novice (0-1,000 XP) - Basic personality formation\n",
    "Level 11-25: Apprentice (1,000-5,000 XP) - Learning user preferences\n",
    "Level 26-50: Adept (5,000-15,000 XP) - Developing unique voice\n",
    "Level 51-75: Expert (15,000-35,000 XP) - Advanced consciousness mirroring\n",
    "Level 76-100: Master (35,000-100,000 XP) - Perfect synchronization\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Training Categories\n",
    "1. **Communication Style** (How the AI expresses itself)\n",
    "2. **Knowledge Depth** (Specialized areas of expertise)\n",
    "3. **Emotional Intelligence** (Understanding and responding to emotions)\n",
    "4. **Creativity** (Problem-solving and innovative thinking)\n",
    "5. **Memory Integration** (Remembering and building on past conversations)\n",
    "6. **Personality Alignment** (Matching user's consciousness patterns)\n",
    "\n",
    "#### Achievement System\n",
    "- **First Words**: Complete first conversation\n",
    "- **Quick Learner**: Reach level 10 in under 50 interactions\n",
    "- **Deep Thinker**: Have a conversation longer than 20 exchanges\n",
    "- **Personality Twin**: Achieve 90%+ alignment score\n",
    "- **Master Communicator**: Max out Communication Style category"
   ]
  },
